# Automated Cold Email Agent (n8n)

An end-to-end cold email automation system built using n8n, Google Sheets, and Gmail.  
This workflow sends personalized emails to multiple leads, tracks delivery status, and logs results automatically.

---

## Project Overview

This project automates the process of sending cold emails by:
- Fetching leads from Google Sheets
- Reading email templates dynamically
- Sending emails via Gmail
- Logging email status and timestamps back into Google Sheets

It is designed to reduce manual outreach effort and ensure consistent email tracking.

---

## Workflow Breakdown

### Trigger
- Workflow starts when the "Test workflow" button is clicked.
- Can be replaced with a Cron trigger for scheduled campaigns.

### Get Leads from Google Sheets
- Reads lead data such as Name, Email, Status, and Time.
- Each row represents one recipient.

### IF Condition
- Filters leads to avoid sending duplicate or unnecessary emails.

### Loop Over Items
- Processes each lead one-by-one.
- Ensures controlled email sending.

### Get Email Templates
- Fetches email templates from a separate Google Sheet.
- Templates can be edited without modifying workflow logic.

### Code Node
- Dynamically personalizes email content.
- Injects variables like recipient name and subject line.

### Merge & Edit Fields
- Combines lead data and email template data.
- Maps required fields for Gmail.

### Send Email via Gmail
- Sends personalized emails using Gmail API.

### Wait Node
- Adds delay between emails to avoid spam detection.

### Log Status
- Updates Google Sheets with:
  - Send status (SENT / UNREAD)
  - Timestamp

---

## Google Sheets Structure

### Leads Sheet
- Name
- Email
- Send Status
- Time

### Templates Sheet
- Subject
- Email Body

---

